sequenceDiagram
autonumber

participant Main as agent/main.go
participant Config as config.Load
participant System as system.Collect
participant Discovery as discovery.Discoverer
participant Metrics as metrics.Collect
participant HTTP as httpclient.Client
participant Backend as Backend API

Main->>Config: 读取节点名、版本、时间间隔

Main->>System: Collect hostname / IP / OS
Main->>Discovery: 执行 ps 与 ss -ltnp
Discovery-->>Main: 已识别服务目录
Main->>HTTP: POST /api/agents/register
HTTP->>Backend: RegisterPayload
Backend-->>HTTP: NodeDetailResponse

Main->>Metrics: 首次采集 CPU / 内存 / 磁盘 / 网络
Main->>HTTP: POST /api/agents/heartbeat
HTTP->>Backend: HeartbeatRequest
Backend-->>HTTP: NodeSummaryResponse

loop 每 15 秒
  Main->>System: Collect hostname / IP / OS
  Main->>Discovery: 重新扫描进程与监听端口
  Discovery-->>Main: 更新服务目录
  Main->>HTTP: POST /api/agents/register
  HTTP->>Backend: RegisterPayload
  Backend-->>HTTP: NodeDetailResponse
end

loop 每 10 秒
  Main->>Metrics: 采集资源指标
  Main->>HTTP: POST /api/agents/heartbeat
  HTTP->>Backend: HeartbeatRequest
  Backend-->>HTTP: NodeSummaryResponse
end

note over Backend: register 更新节点与服务目录\nheartbeat 更新状态、心跳时间与资源时序
